  • Constructor Details

    • SaveObject

      public SaveObject(short type, short invasive, short site, double locationX, double locationY)

      Constructor to save a cell as object.

      Parameters:
      type - The type of the cell (0 = sensitive, 1 = resistant)
      invasive - Wether or not the cell is invasive (0 = non-invasive, 1 = invasive)
      site - The site in which the cell is located (0 = solid tumor)
      locationX - Location of the cell on the X axis
      locationY - Location of the cell on the y axis
